                "code": "patient-history"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "subject": {
          "reference": "urn:uuid:11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
        },
        "payload": [
          {
            "contentString": "{patientName} has no significant past medical history. He was born at full term via normal vaginal delivery without complications. He has had no prior hospitalizations or surgeries. He experienced one episode of otitis media at age 4, which resolved with a short course of antibiotics. {patientName} has no known drug allergies aside from a mild food intolerance to shellfish. His developmental milestones have all been met on time. Family history is notable for allergic rhinitis in his mother and asthma in a paternal uncle. {patientName}'s immunizations are current, including annual influenza vaccination. He lives in a non-smoking household and attends a public school with approximately 25 children in his class, providing significant exposure to common childhood viral pathogens."
          }
        ]
      }
    }
